      linarith [h2, h3]
    _ = (c / p) * (eLorentzNorm (fun x => (f x).re) p 1 μ + eLorentzNorm (fun x => (f x).im) p 1 μ) * ν G ^ p'⁻¹.toReal := by
      ring
    _ = (c / p) * eLorentzNorm f p 1 μ * ν G ^ p'⁻¹.toReal := by
      rw [h4]
      <;> ring
    _ = (4 * c / p) * eLorentzNorm f p 1 μ * ν G ^ p'⁻¹.toReal := by
      ring_nf
```

